[{"id":813228,"node":"职场话题","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/career","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/4ea0/6fbc/770_mini.png?m=1635744526","description":"如题。<br />1. 信息部远程别人电脑的时候，对方会有提示，桌面背景会变成黑色。<br />2. 工作有的时候很忙，最近确实不忙。<br />3. 我工位在过道，他们来信息部办事，都能看到我屏幕。","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/813228","replies":119,"created_ts":1636080622,"created":"10:50:22","title":"我是公司信息部运维，有些工作是要远程同事的电脑处理问题。\r\n昨天远程 A 同事的电脑时，无意间看到 B 同事在企业微信跟 A 聊天，指名道姓说我天天没事干偷窥别人。\r\n聊天记录已截图，请问我该怎么办？经理说让我大度点，算了。","author":"BottleKay","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/BottleKay","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/13f0db4c6c301a0dbdfd7762b1520bc2?s=24&d=retro"},{"id":813186,"node":"iPhone","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/iphone","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c9f0/f895/8_mini.png?m=1630643991","description":"","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/813186","replies":105,"created_ts":1636074127,"created":"09:02:07","title":"为什么 iPhone 不做主题商店？","author":"FridayToGo","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/FridayToGo","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/c53a/4efb/380169_mini.png?m=1548404955"},{"id":813277,"node":"Apple","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/apple","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6cdd/60ea/184_mini.png?m=1630643913","description":"上周去店里试戴了一下，回来对着 AirPods Pro ，可以说是茶不思饭不想了，音质太香了，有朋友分享下使用日常吗","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/813277","replies":76,"created_ts":1636093983,"created":"14:33:03","title":"朋友们，一年了，终于想起买 AirPods Max，有劝退的吗","author":"IM1T","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/IM1T","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/fae1a48d2f19d73b35b1332f93807fda?s=24&d=retro"},{"id":813358,"node":"全球工单系统","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/gts","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/74bb/a227/938_mini.png?m=1591791660","description":"<p>firefox 国际版， 主页更改为 bing</p>\n<p>刚发现首页被私自改了，改成特供版了</p>\n<p>恶心啊！恶心！ xxxxxxxx</p>\n<p>不要跟 edge 比烂了</p>\n<p><img alt=\"图片.png\" class=\"embedded_image\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" rel=\"noreferrer\" src=\"https://i.loli.net/2021/11/05/qZVWShRA7TOPXmc.png\"/></p>\n<p><img alt=\"图片.png\" class=\"embedded_image\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" rel=\"noreferrer\" src=\"https://i.loli.net/2021/11/05/BHYMnNqUEo9GLk6.png\"/></p>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/813358","replies":70,"created_ts":1636110212,"created":"19:03:32","title":"火狐也开始摆烂了","author":"hwdef","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/hwdef","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/5cad/004d/187144_mini.png?m=1636109950"},{"id":813275,"node":"Redis","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/redis","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/67c6/a1e7/47_mini.png?m=1608052197","description":"<p>问这个是因为我们公司目前的方法 我觉得挺不妥的 然后我也没有接触过别的公司或者并发比较大的系统中如何存储以及如何读取 redis</p>\n<p>使用 redisson 连接的 redis(哨兵)</p>\n<p>目前是存人群信息, 分了 1000 个 key (redis 中 key 如果很多的话会有问题么)</p>\n<p>1000 个 key 的 value 是 一个大 Map ,存取这个 map 用的是 getLocalCachedMap</p>\n<p>map 的每个 key 对应一个人 value 就是他的数据(数据量肯定不大 几百 k 吧)</p>\n<p>然后业务集群每天大概请求在 40 -50 亿 然后峰值是 70 亿(其中也会过滤一些请求 比如不合法的或者各种过滤条件过滤掉),剩下的基本每次请求都会去请求一下 Redis 拿用户数据</p>\n<p>这样一个 map 的话就会存多个人群数据 这样子维护的话 不会混乱么 比如有的人更新了有的人数据没更新</p>\n<p>大家有做过类似的这种 redis 数据维护么 我也想了解了解</p>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/813275","replies":65,"created_ts":1636093776,"created":"14:29:36","title":"Redis 到底应该怎么存储使用?","author":"chengouzi","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/chengouzi","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/029349f865354d5d93c55a675e4c221d?s=24&d=retro"},{"id":813235,"node":" WATCH","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/watch","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/3b5d/ca50/819_mini.png?m=1633251402","description":"","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/813235","replies":63,"created_ts":1636082358,"created":"11:19:18","title":"aw7 刚刚收到，求推荐睡眠监测软件","author":"yuhuan66666","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/yuhuan66666","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/6840671dff0dd2c7676f1d1e4b2cb046?s=24&d=retro"},{"id":813262,"node":"职场话题","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/career","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/4ea0/6fbc/770_mini.png?m=1635744526","description":"<p>活久见。。。一口老血吐出来</p>\n<p>离职提前四周通知，我上周提的，老板同意了。现在还剩三周要走了，又让我开新项目，我跟他说时间不够，他竟然 push 我说“我知道你要走了，所以没那么投入了，好好干可以完成的”</p>\n<p>这种情况该怎么安排交接和离职啊？我的想法是找个同事一起弄，我负责 30%-40%的工作量，剩下的提前跟同事交代好，离职以后就交接给他了</p>\n<p>大家有什么更好的办法么？想体面一些，因为保不齐以后要找这个雇主帮忙出介绍信</p>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/813262","replies":62,"created_ts":1636090822,"created":"13:40:22","title":"还有三周离职，老板叫我开发个新项目","author":"ohce","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/ohce","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/69c05e513fd405089b7bf57853b3e0c8?s=24&d=retro"},{"id":813173,"node":"MacBook Pro","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/mbp","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/d3d9/4468/10_mini.png?m=1630643933","description":"我是 M1 max 16 寸款，电池差不多只能用 10 小时以下<br /><br />详细评测： <div class=\"embedded_video_wrapper\"><iframe src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/PfeFuAFoCs0\" class=\"embedded_video\" allowfullscreen=\"\" type=\"text/html\" id=\"ytplayer\" frameborder=\"0\"></iframe></div>","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/813173","replies":57,"created_ts":1636049068,"created":"02:04:28","title":"M1 Max 对比 M1 Pro 电池续航对比的详细评测出来了","author":"MID","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/MID","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/20af/c7ff/523581_mini.png?m=1607843072"},{"id":813270,"node":"macOS","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/macos","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/b6d7/67d2/22_mini.png?m=1635652519","description":"PDF Expert 内存占用巨大，开个 textbook 就有两 G 左右的占用…… Preview 是好用，但是不支持双页连续翻滚","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/813270","replies":56,"created_ts":1636092715,"created":"14:11:55","title":"M1 有啥好用的 PDF 阅读器","author":"rzbyy","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/rzbyy","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/1064/3af8/560031_mini.png?m=1636092618"},{"id":813188,"node":"问与答","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/qna","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_mini.png?m=1629391393","description":"在校大二学生，h 之前填完那个申请后，一直没有后文了，也想玩一玩试一试，想问下什么渠道可以用上","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/813188","replies":51,"created_ts":1636074676,"created":"09:11:16","title":"请问各位是怎么申请到 copilot 的？","author":"Lagrangist","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/Lagrangist","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/84e993fa9bacb21845cfa8a300e3fad7?s=24&d=retro"},{"id":813253,"node":"编辑器","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/editors","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/7407/1a67/477_mini.png?m=1439978846","description":"<p>只讨论前端领域，感觉 vscode 的更新迭代越来越频繁，对各种新技术的支持和开发体验方面也做得越来越好，而且还出了在线版，综合体验已经超过 webstorm 了。当然对于 java ，idea 肯定还是天花板，但未来不排除被 vscode 赶超的可能。大家怎么看呢？</p>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/813253","replies":48,"created_ts":1636087370,"created":"12:42:50","title":"大家觉得，前端领域 vscode 现在超越 webstorm（包括 idea 全家桶）了吗？","author":"fengmengqiu","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/fengmengqiu","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/1b29/2d95/107453_mini.png?m=1636086778"},{"id":813203,"node":"奇思妙想","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/ideas","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6353/8fe6/519_mini.png?m=1595507885","description":"<p>主要是从设计层面或者说理念层面考虑这个问题，感觉现在绝大多数的浏览器打开主页都是信息流，包括 chrome 、edge 等等，可是从逻辑上来说，信息流并不是浏览器应该做的事情，之所以现在信息流普遍泛滥，主要是由于字节公司的信息流产品对人产生的强大的粘性（瘾）所产生的示范效应。\n浏览器是互联网的入口，其主页也应被视为手机的主屏幕，而所保存的书签其实也就等于下载的应用，因此主页首要的任务应该是显示我的书签，形式甚至可以和现在的手机操作系统一致，图标，名称，文件夹，拖动排序等等，其次是才是信息流，而这里的信息流应该是我所保存书签的通知或者说是 rss ，这就相当于手机系统中 app 的通知了，最后是导航，很自然的，在这样的理念下导航就等于手机操作系统的软件商店...\n总结来说就是用手机操作系统的逻辑重新看待和设计浏览器，不知此想法是否有问题，欢迎大家交流。</p>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/813203","replies":45,"created_ts":1636077833,"created":"10:03:53","title":"是不是应该把浏览器也看做操作系统？","author":"oncetalk","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/oncetalk","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/a91b/01ba/480979_mini.png?m=1636075826"},{"id":813404,"node":"信息安全","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/security","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/a4f2/3670/260_mini.png?m=1633245702","description":"<p>才发现原来 1password 家庭版车主的权利那么大\n可以随意的停止账号，甚至删除账号，成员就直接登陆不上了</p>\n<p>为什么还是那么多人随便找车就上了，不害怕被删么</p>\n<p>你说找熟悉的朋友那些 还说得过去。。。</p>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/813404","replies":42,"created_ts":1636127224,"created":"23:47:04","title":"1password 家庭版车主可以随意停止和删除成员账号，为什么还是那么多人随便找车上？","author":"iamjerry","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/iamjerry","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/92799cdf8322ad9603db7440b59c55b5?s=24&d=retro"},{"id":813322,"node":"微软","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/microsoft","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/afd4/8367/699_mini.png?m=1367518397","description":"<p>楼主因为工作原因使用了较长时间 Teams 办公，不懂就问，为啥作为一个大厂的生产力软件显得不太好用，远不如 Office 系列其他软件好用：</p>\n<ol>\n<li>太卡，滑动聊天窗口会有明显的加载延迟 （网络也许是原因之一，但是连着微软内网都卡...）</li>\n<li>容易 crash ，平均一周会出现一次明显卡死，只能杀掉重开</li>\n<li>中英文混合输入时容易出现显示异常</li>\n</ol>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/813322","replies":38,"created_ts":1636101510,"created":"16:38:30","title":"为啥 Teams 这么难用","author":"MinoZhao","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/MinoZhao","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/5813b6031c6b327cdd1a54637cd214ec?s=24&d=retro"},{"id":813402,"node":"Apple","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/apple","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6cdd/60ea/184_mini.png?m=1630643913","description":"","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/813402","replies":28,"created_ts":1636126434,"created":"23:33:54","title":"谣传 iPad mini 6 要上高刷屏，在等蜂窝版的兄弟们 hold 住啊！","author":"Borden","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/Borden","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/e131/5e5e/96842_mini.png?m=1635353502"}]